metadata.name: MY EYES
metadata.description:
All the world was spinning forward in the orbit of logics.
My mind, my heart and my eyes were decided to regain all of their power and strength to spin in the opposite direction in the orbit. 

My beliefs and faith turned their faces around from logics and moved to the side that my heart stands; where my art comes from.
Now I'm a human who doesn't care about his mind and goes forward to the future with his heart and love. 

The designs that my fingers designing are my emotions feedbacks in this universe. 

Spinning orbits of the solar system is around the Sun, but the desires of my heart were so against it that maybe I had created another galaxy for my self.
A galaxy made out of Me, my heart and my pen which I design with. 

I'm here to create my own universe and my own galaxy by my designs.
